# Lemongrass Tofu Banh Mi

Based on [School Night Vegan - Easy Tofu Marinades](https://schoolnightvegan.com/home/easy-tofu-marinades/) and [Lazy Cat Kitchen - Lemongrass Tofu](https://www.lazycatkitchen.com/lemongrass-tofu/)

